metadata.name: POSTER.SINGLE.HEALING_STILL._004
metadata.description:
HEALING, STILL → INTERNAL MISALIGNMENTS. UNRELEASED VARIANT OF TRACK 04 FROM THE WASTED POTENTIAL E.P ORIGINALLY TITLED "HEALING". 

↓ 

THE REST OF IT is a collection of posters for tracks that didn't make it onto my debut E.P titled WASTED POTENTIAL. All these songs started as journal entries, as spoken words & poems for my sanity. These posters & their sounds are pages from chapters yet to be finished.

↓
